categories: Category:Grand Army of the Republic squads

nodes.text: Wesk Squad was a squad of Advanced Recon Force troopers who fought in the Third battle of Felucia. During this battle, the squad sent out a message to the Galactic Republic outpost on Felucia, requesting assistance in transporting some supplies back to base. Not long after sending the message, a Jedi Knight was sent to take the supplies to the outpost.
